241
00:19:42,450 --> 00:19:44,431
Tamak betul kau.

242
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:48,700
Betul tu. Saya memang tamak.

243
00:20:14,840 --> 00:20:16,630
Makhluk yang tamak...

244
00:20:18,100 --> 00:20:20,360
Makhluk yang makan dosa-dosa saya...

245
00:20:21,760 --> 00:20:22,990
Saya berterima kasih.

246
00:20:23,910 --> 00:20:25,735
Sekarang, saya tidak lagi...

247
00:20:27,035 --> 00:20:28,540
...rasa lapar.

248
00:20:34,960 --> 00:20:36,320
Disahkan.

